  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the daydreams of a child, exploring the seas of his imagination as you brave the dangers of a pirate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander the waves as you attack, board and sink ships to amass your own fortune! Will you prefer approaching the battles wearing down your opponent from a distance with powerful cannons, rush them aboard to prove your skill with the sword, or maybe some more... brutal meeting using the prow?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your ability to manage the various parts of a ship: sails, helm, repairs, cannons... Recruit cat sailors for your crew who will assist you in those various tasks, as long as they don't blow up something!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.poster.avif?t=1727999896\" width=592 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.webm?t=1727999896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.mp4?t=1727999896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naval combat and piloting</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruitment of a feline crew</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail in a 3D world, with a 2D artstyle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist and follow to support this solo dev project! </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the daydreams of a child, exploring the seas of his imagination as you brave the dangers of a pirate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander the waves as you attack, board and sink ships to amass your own fortune! Will you prefer approaching the battles wearing down your opponent from a distance with powerful cannons, rush them aboard to prove your skill with the sword, or maybe some more... brutal meeting using the prow?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your ability to manage the various parts of a ship: sails, helm, repairs, cannons... Recruit cat sailors for your crew who will assist you in those various tasks, as long as they don't blow up something!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.poster.avif?t=1727999896\" width=592 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.webm?t=1727999896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721040/extras/f12dd95e71790a8a65211f5106e90205.mp4?t=1727999896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naval combat and piloting</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruitment of a feline crew</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail in a 3D world, with a 2D artstyle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist and follow to support this solo dev project! </p>",
